This lists the most important features of FreeBSD-bot.
The non-important stuff will be weeded out from the bot altogether
at some point in the near future.

Port Lookup:
   <category/portname>


## Future Commands:

Port Search:
   <keyword:[terms]>
   <maintainer:[terms]>
   <desc:[terms]> or <description:[terms]>

ManPage Lookup:
   !man [command]
   <man:[command]>

FreeBSD Forums:
   <forums:[topic_id]>
   <forums:[topic_id].[postnumber]>
   !forums [topic_id]
   !forms [topic_id] [postnumber]
